We present you the first online competition of Converge'18.
The 2018 edition of
"Once Upon A Time in JIIT"

All you have to do is post your untold interesting college stories on your Facebook profiles. Small task to fetch you huge prizes.

...

Rules:
1) Post your story and tag
Converge page as well as use #converge2k18 #WhereMagicHappens.
2) Points Division:
Like: 1 point
Comment: 2 points
Share: 5 points
3) Last day of entry is Sunday, 11:59pm.
4) Results will be announced on Monday.

Note: Entries will be prohibited if they do not adhere to any of the above mentioned rules.
